  "title": "Part-Time Event & Retail Staff",
  "description": "<p>🍎🍊 Part-Time Event & Retail Staff🍓 Fruit Pop-Up Store 🍇<br /><br /><strong>📍 Location:</strong> Various event venues / pop-up locations<br /><strong>⏰ Working Hours:</strong> Flexible shifts (including weekends & public holidays)<br /><strong>📄 Employment Type:</strong> Part-time / Event-based<br /><br /><strong>🧺 Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />🍉 Assist with <strong>set-up and tear-down</strong> of fruit pop-up stalls (tables, displays, signage)<br />🍊 <strong>Pack, handle & display fruits</strong> neatly and hygienically<br />🍎 Ensure fruits are <strong>fresh, attractive & well-labelled</strong><br />🛍️ <strong>Manning the store</strong> and attending to walk-in customers<br />😊 Provide <strong>friendly customer service</strong> and basic fruit knowledge</p><p><p>💰 Assist with <strong>sales transactions</strong> (Cash/PayNow)</p></p><p><p>🧹 Maintain <strong>cleanliness and organisation</strong> of the stall</p></p><p><p>📦 Support <strong>stock counting, replenishment & simple inventory checks</strong></p></p><p><p>🧤 Follow <strong>food hygiene & safety standards</strong></p></p><p><p>🔧 Handle <strong>other ad-hoc retail or event duties</strong> as needed</p></p><h3>✅ Requirements:</h3><p><p>😄 Positive attitude & <strong>willingness to learn</strong></p></p><p><p>💪 Able to <strong>stand for long hours</strong> and do light lifting</p></p><p><p>🗣️ Comfortable talking to customers of all ages</p></p><p><p>⏱️ <strong>Reliable, punctual & responsible</strong></p></p><p><p>🛒 Retail or event experience is a <strong>plus but not required</strong></p></p><p><p>🌏 Basic English communication skills<br /><em>(Mandarin or dialects is a bonus 🍊)</em></p></p><h3>🎁 What We Offer:</h3><p><p>💵 Competitive hourly pay</p></p><p><p>🕒 Flexible working schedule</p></p><p><p>🎪 Hands-on event & retail experience</p></p><p><p>🤝 Friendly and supportive team environment</p></p>",
