    "description": "<p><strong>Sandhu ImpEx Pte. Ltd.</strong> is a Singapore-based trading company specialising in the import, export, transhipment, wholesale, and retail of premium fresh produce. Through our flagship brand <strong>ISTANA Royal Fruits</strong>, we curate a wide selection of seasonal, tropical, and exotic fruits sourced from trusted growers to ensure consistent quality, freshness, and taste. Registered with the Singapore Food Authority and Singapore Customs as importers, we serve both B2B and retail customers with efficient logistics, transparent pricing, and reliable delivery across Singapore and the region. Our commitment is simple: dependable supply, uncompromising standards, and long-term partnerships built on trust.</p>",
